issue.title: Project doesn't load
issue.body:
When I open the Localization solution, the project doesn't load and outputs this error:
'maui-samples-main\7.0\Fundamentals\Localization\LocalizationDemo\LocalizationDemo.csproj : error  : Duplicated folder item found in the project: "Platforms\Android\Resources\drawable-es\flag.png".'

issue.body:

1. Minimize net maui app to tray 
2. Context Menu support on Tray Icon right click

Windows MacOS

https://github.com/dotnet/maui-samples/tree/main/7.0/Apps/WeatherTwentyOne/src/WeatherTwentyOne/Platforms/Windows
